RepairImpactKind RepairImpactKind Enum

In this Article

Edit

Specifies the kind of the RepairImpactDescription.

This type supports the Service Fabric platform; it is not meant to be used directly from your code.

Syntax

Declaration

public enum RepairImpactKindPublic Enum RepairImpactKind

Fields

Invalid
Invalid

The repair impact is not valid or is of an unknown type.
Node
Node

The repair impact affects a set of Service Fabric nodes.

Details
